## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="832c9-286"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 대/소문자 구분 조회를 먼저 수행합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="832c9-286"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> performs a case-sensitive lookup first.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="832c9-287">실패 한 경우에 두 번째 대/소문자 구분 검색이 수행 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="832c9-287">If it fails, a second case-insensitive search is made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="832c9-288">메서드에서 throw 된 `IndexOutOfRange` 서 수는 0부터 시작 하는 열을 찾을 수 없는 경우 예외입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="832c9-288">The method throws an `IndexOutOfRange` exception if the zero-based column ordinal is not found.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="832c9-289"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 가 되지 일본어가 나 너비 구분 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="832c9-289"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> is kana-width insensitive.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="832c9-290">서 수 기반 조회가 명명 된 조회 보다 효율적 이므로, 것이 없습니다 효율적 호출 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 루프 내에서.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="832c9-290">Because ordinal-based lookups are more efficient than named lookups, it is inefficient to call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> within a loop.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="832c9-291">대신, 호출 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 루프 내에서 결과 대 한 정수 변수를 사용 하 여 한 번 및 할당 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="832c9-291">Instead, call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> once and then assign the results to an integer variable for use within the loop.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="832c9-292">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 메서드를 사용하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="832c9-292">The following example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub ReadOracleData(ByVal connectionString As String)  
  
    Dim queryString As String = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders"  
    Dim connection As New OracleConnection(connectionString)  
    Dim command As New OracleCommand(queryString, connectionString)  
  
    connection.Open()  
  
    Dim reader As OracleDataReader = command.ExecuteReader()  
  
    Dim custIdCol As Integer = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID")  
  
    Do While reader.Read()  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol))  
    Loop  
  
    reader.Close()  
    connection.Close()  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void ReadOracleData(string connectionString)  
{  
    string queryString = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders";  
    OracleConnection connection = new OracleConnection(connectionString);  
    OracleCommand command = new OracleCommand(queryString,connection);  
  
    connection.Open();  
    OracleDataReader reader = command.ExecuteReader();  
  
    int custIdCol = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID");  
  
    while (reader.Read())  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol));  
  
    reader.Close();  
    connection.Close();  
}  
```
